<html><head><meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=utf-8" /><meta http-equiv="Content-Style-Type" content="text/css" /><meta name="generator" content="Aspose.Words for .NET 13.4.0.0" /><title>[Committee name]</title></head><body><div><p style="font-size:12pt; line-height:200%; margin:0pt; text-align:justify"><span style="font-family:Garamond; font-size:12pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="line-height:28pt; margin:14pt 0pt 9pt"><span style="color:#002855; font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 55 Roman'; font-size:20pt">Joint Committee on Human Rights</span></p><p style="line-height:28pt; margin:14pt 0pt 9pt"><span style="color:#002855; font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 55 Roman'; font-size:18pt">Oral evidence:</span><span style="color:#002855; font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 55 Roman'; font-size:18pt"> </span><a href="http://www.parliament.uk/business/committees/committees-a-z/joint-select/human-rights-committee/inquiries/parliament-2010/judicial-review-reform/"><span style="color:#0000ff; font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 55 Roman'; font-size:18pt; text-decoration:underline">The implications for access to justice of the Government’s proposed judicial review reforms</span></a><span style="color:#002855; font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 55 Roman'; font-size:18pt">, HC </span><span style="color:#002855; font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 55 Roman'; font-size:18pt">868</span><br /><span style="color:#002855; font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 55 Roman'; font-size:18pt">Wednes</span><span style="color:#002855; font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 55 Roman'; font-size:18pt">day </span><span style="color:#002855; font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 55 Roman'; font-size:18pt">4</span><span style="color:#002855; font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 55 Roman'; font-size:18pt"> </span><span style="color:#002855; font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 55 Roman'; font-size:18pt">Decem</span><span style="color:#002855; font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 55 Roman'; font-size:18pt">ber 2013</span></p><p style="margin:0pt 0pt 12pt; text-alig